text: Wang Jianxun (born 4 November 1981) is a Chinese ski jumper. He competed in the large hill team event at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of China Category:Ski jumpers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:People from Tonghua
